Your instincts take over and you immediately burst into motion, performing four different actions simultaneously.First, you drop lower to the ground and start running for the train at full speed. 
Second, your hand immediately goes for your gun. Third and fourth, quickly shutting one of your eyes as your other hand throws a small flashbang grenade in the direction of the attacker.
The tiny grenade explodes a split second before you've passed through the train doors, temporarily blinding you in your still open eye and giving you a nasty headache. 
Without slowing down, you switch over to your other eye. As fast as you are, however, you still clipped your shoulder on the doorframe as you run past it.#
